        <category domain="category" nicename="food"><![CDATA[Food]]></category>
        <category domain="post_tag" nicename="recipes"><![CDATA[Recipes]]></category>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Mediterranean cuisine is healthy, flavorful, and surprisingly simple. These recipes have become my weeknight staples.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">Quick Greek Salad</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Fresh tomatoes, cucumbers, red onion, olives, and feta with olive oil and lemon. Ready in 10 minutes.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Simple Pasta</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Cherry tomatoes, garlic, fresh basil, and good olive oil. Toss with pasta and finish with parmesan. Comfort food at its finest.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Use quality ingredients</li>
<li>Don't overcomplicate</li>
<li>Let flavors shine</li>
<li>Fresh herbs make a difference</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Simple, delicious Mediterranean recipes for busy weeknights.]]></excerpt:encoded>
    </item>

    <!-- Blog Post 4 -->
    <item>
        <title>Finding Balance in a Busy World</title>
        <link>https://demos.codoplex.com/versana/blog/finding-balance</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 09:15:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
        <wp:post_id>13</wp:post_id>
        <wp:post_date>2024-02-27 09:15:00</wp:post_date>
        <wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
        <wp:status>publish</wp:status>
        <wp:post_name>finding-balance</wp:post_name>
        <category domain="category" nicename="lifestyle"><![CDATA[Lifestyle]]></category>
        <category domain="post_tag" nicename="mindfulness"><![CDATA[Mindfulness]]></category>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Balance isn't about perfect equilibrium—it's about making intentional choices that align with your values and priorities.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">What Balance Really Means</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Some days work gets more attention. Other days focus on family or self-care. The key is being present wherever you are.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Simple Strategies</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Set boundaries around work time</li>
<li>Schedule activities you enjoy</li>
<li>Learn to say no without guilt</li>
<li>Take breaks throughout the day</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Balance looks different for everyone. Experiment to find what works for your life and circumstances.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Practical strategies for finding balance in modern life.]]></excerpt:encoded>
    </item>

    <!-- Blog Post 5 -->
    <item>
        <title>Books That Changed My Perspective</title>
        <link>https://demos.codoplex.com/versana/blog/transformative-books</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 02 Mar 2024 14:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
        <wp:post_id>14</wp:post_id>
        <wp:post_date>2024-03-02 14:30:00</wp:post_date>
        <wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
        <wp:status>publish</wp:status>
        <wp:post_name>transformative-books</wp:post_name>
        <category domain="category" nicename="lifestyle"><![CDATA[Lifestyle]]></category>
        <category domain="post_tag" nicename="books"><![CDATA[Books]]></category>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Certain books arrive at exactly the right moment and shift how we see the world. Here are five that profoundly impacted me.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">On Personal Growth</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Books about mindset, habits, and self-awareness opened my eyes to possibilities I hadn't considered. They sparked real change.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Fiction That Resonates</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Sometimes fiction teaches deeper truths than nonfiction. Stories that explore human nature and connection stay with us long after the final page.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Read widely across genres</li>
<li>Don't force books you're not enjoying</li>
<li>Take notes on ideas that resonate</li>
<li>Apply lessons to your life</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Five books that shifted my perspective and inspired personal growth.]]></excerpt:encoded>
    </item>

    <!-- Blog Post 6 -->
    <item>
        <title>Home Office Setup Tips</title>
        <link>https://demos.codoplex.com/versana/blog/home-office-setup</link>
        <pubDate>Wed, 06 Mar 2024 11:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[admin]]></dc:creator>
        <wp:post_id>15</wp:post_id>
        <wp:post_date>2024-03-06 11:00:00</wp:post_date>
        <wp:post_type>post</wp:post_type>
        <wp:status>publish</wp:status>
        <wp:post_name>home-office-setup</wp:post_name>
        <category domain="category" nicename="lifestyle"><![CDATA[Lifestyle]]></category>
        <category domain="post_tag" nicename="productivity"><![CDATA[Productivity]]></category>
        <content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Your workspace dramatically impacts productivity and mood. After years of trial and error, here's what actually matters.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading -->
<h2 class="wp-block-heading">The Essentials</h2>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Good chair, proper lighting, and organized desk make the biggest difference. Everything else is optional but nice to have.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:heading {"level":3} -->
<h3 class="wp-block-heading">Creating the Right Environment</h3>
<!-- /wp:heading -->

<!-- wp:list -->
<ul class="wp-block-list">
<li>Natural light whenever possible</li>
<li>Minimal clutter and distractions</li>
<li>Plants for air quality and mood</li>
<li>Personal touches that inspire</li>
</ul>
<!-- /wp:list -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Invest in what supports your health and work. A quality chair and monitor stand prevent discomfort and boost focus.</p>
<!-- /wp:paragraph -->]]></content:encoded>
        <excerpt:encoded><![CDATA[Essential tips for creating a productive and comfortable home office space.]]></excerpt:encoded>
    </item>

